{"title":"大海（外一首）","authors":["钟永华"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":3,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟永华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条条溪流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一层层浪叠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾不息地汇入这"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌动的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海呵，正敞开博大的胸襟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"容纳着所有的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风，山色，云霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光，朗月，星座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及混沌、污浊和败草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海，不是以其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自身的信念和价值"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗涤着，沉淀着，净化着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切龌龊和芜秽吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而光波和亮色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在不断跃动的潮汐中泛着透明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呈出碧绿了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知哪天早上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿冒出一片又一片森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莽莽苍苍的森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莽莽森林间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有那么多的花簇、云霓、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星光和鸟群　以及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七彩的光鲜和流行色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上掉下新大陆了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游客纷至沓来"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}